The fields of hegemonic Knowledge, Design and Technology have not been sufficiently influenced from perspectives coming from the Global South and or Tropical Areas, this exchange is still pending. Consumer-grade GPU nodes are invited to join the network without permission, enabling them to mine the native token, $HYPT, by performing PoUW tasks such as AI inference and 3D rendering.
